<body>
<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1038150" n="1"/> <pb facs="1038151" n="2"/> <pb facs="1038152" n="3"/> <pb facs="1038153" n="4"/>
<opener><salute><lb/>Viro <abbr>pl.</abbr> Reverendo ac Celeberrimo
  <lb/><rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-119112450" >Jacobo Hermanno</rs>
  <lb/><abbr>N. B. S. P. D.</abbr></salute></opener>
<p><lb/>Quanquam amicitia nostra non<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stimanda est ex frequentia
  <lb/>litterarum nostrarum, tamen nolui committere ut diutius expectares respon<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>sionem meam ad litteras tuas gratissimas, quas <date>mense Junio
  <lb/>superioris anni</date> accepi, pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sertim quia me nunc plures, quam
  <lb/>hactenus, caus<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> ad scribendum impellunt. <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>quum enim esse
  <lb/>duxi, ut tibi significarem, me sub initium hujus anni misisse
  <lb/>ad <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118509969">Patruum</rs> tentamen solutionis generalis <rs type="keyword">Problematis traje<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ctoriarum</rs>, ut si dignum judicaret <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-2879139">Lipsiam</rs> transmitteret,
  <lb/>In isto Schediasmate mo deste monui, quid in solutione tua
  <lb/>generali, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <date>mense Julio superioris anni</date> <rs type="biblio">Actis</rs> inserta est,
  <lb/>desiderem, roga vique ut errorem, quem in regulam tuam
  <lb/>irrepsisse credo, corrigeres aut ejusdem regul<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> sensum plenius expli<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>cares. Te autem petitionem meam jam pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>venisse suspicor ex his
  <lb/>qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> mihi <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118509969">Patruus</rs> nuper ex <rs type="letter">epistola</rs> aliqua tua excerpta transmi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>sit, verbis tuis: "trajectori<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> per quadraturas in transcendentibus
  <lb/>generaliter describi non possunt, et ego modum demum inveni qui
  <lb/>ad dissimiles curvas transcen dentes <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>que ac similes sese extendit,
  <lb/>cujus specimen dedi in eadem scheda qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> in <rs type="biblio">Actis</rs> hujus mensis <date>Ja<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nuarii</date> comparebit. Rogabo igitur <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118509969">Patruum</rs>, ut scriptum
  <lb/>meum tecum, si fieri possit, communicandum curet antequam
  <lb/>imprimatur, ut id, si nihil scitu dignum illud continere
  <lb/>reperias, supprimas omnino, aut saltem illi, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> monenda
  <pb facs="1038151" n="2"/>
  <lb/>habebis, adjungas. Ceterum gaudeo, quod nunc agnoscas, tra<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>jectorias per quadraturas in transcendentibus generaliter descri<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>bi non posse; sed rectius dixisses, si omisisses verba h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>c
  <lb/><hi rend="u">in transcendentibus</hi>, nam meo quidem judicio in <hi rend="u">alge<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>braicis</hi> quoque trajectori<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> generaliter per quadraturas
  <lb/>describi nequeunt. Rogo autem, ut omnia, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> in hanc rem
  <lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> me dicta sunt, boni consules. </p>
<p> Vidi <rs type="biblio">Offenburgii Schediasma</rs>
  <lb/>quo <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1089923198">Verzali<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> <rs type="letter">epistolam</rs> pulchre depexuit; sed puto me hu<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>jus rei poenam ferre; nebulo enim iste, me forte Offen<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>burgium esse judicans, contra me sub persona <hi rend="u"><rs type="person">Caroli Bal<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>di</rs></hi> in lucem protrusit <rs type="biblio">libellum</rs> famosum duabus plagu<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>lis constantem, simillimum illius quem contra te edidit, ple<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>num contumeliis, ineptiis et paralogismis ultra modum enormibus, quem autem
  <lb/>tuum exemplum secutus responsione nulla, nisi
  <lb/>necessitate coactus, dignabor. Plura sunt qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> mihi persua<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>dent, ut credam non alium quam <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1089923198">Verzaliam</rs> hujus <rs type="biblio">libelli</rs> Aucto<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rem esse, ea autem recensere non opus est. An <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1089923198">Verzalia</rs> Pro<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>blemata duo ab Offenburgio proposita soluturus sit, valde
  <lb/>dubito, pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sertim quod attinet ad posterius; ex occasione au<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tem prioris, quod est de invenienda <rs type="keyword">Catenaria</rs> ex data lege
  <lb/><rs type="keyword">virium centralium</rs> ad centrum finit<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> distanti<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> tendentium,
  <lb/>monere te debeo, ut <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1089923198">Verzali<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> ansam de te trium<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>phandi eripias corrigendo errorem qui est in <rs type="biblio">Phoron.</rs> <abbr>pag.</abbr>
  <lb/>46. et <abbr>pag.</abbr> 382. ubi dicis,
  <lb/>si potenti<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> sint proportionales elementis Curv<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>, et ipsa<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>
  <pb facs="1038152" n="3"/>
  rum directiones concurrant ad punctum finit<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> distanti<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>, Catena<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>riam esse hyperbolam <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>quilateram, cujus centrum in centro<lb/> virium; quod hoc verum esse non possit vel ex eo
  <lb/>solo apparet, quod augendo distantiam centri usque in infini<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tum hyperbola <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>quilatera qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> tandem evadit linea recta deberet evadere Catenaria
  <lb/>vulgaris, et ex curva algebraica in casu particulari mutari in
  <lb/>Curvam transcendentem; jam vero quod curva transcendens sub
  <lb/>curva algebraica tanquam species sub genere comprehendi pos<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>sit, asserere non voles. <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-119291967">Fardellam</rs> jam ante plures
  <lb/>menses diem suum obiisse fortasse non ignorabis. <rs type="person">Petrus</rs> tuus
  <lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> longo tempore mihi non amplius servit, ex quo scilicet è Patria,
  <lb/>quam post mortem <rs type="person">Patris</rs> inviseram, redux apud <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-11887733X">Polenum</rs>
  <lb/>commorari coepi. Monialis aliqua ex monasterio <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs type="person">Catharin<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs>, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
  <lb/>se <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-2661604">Basileensem</rs> esse dicit, mihi <rs type="letter">litteras</rs> cum panibus dulciariis misit
  <lb/>semel atque iterum, credens prima vice se eas mittere tibi, cujus nomen
  <lb/>(male quidem expressum) litteris inscriptum erat; puto autem te non
  <lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>gre laturum, quod munus tibi destinatum ad me vel po<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tius ad <rs type="persons">Polenianos</rs>, quibus illud consumendum dederam, pervenerit.
  <lb/>Junior <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-120379260">Scheuchzerorum</rs> fratrum, amicus noster, quem Collegam
  <lb/>meum fore sperabam, injuriam (dent veniam verbo superi) passus
  <lb/>est non levem; concordibus suffragiis electus erat ab <abbr>Illmis.</abbr>
  <lb/>et <abbr>Exc.</abbr> <abbr>mis.</abbr> Reformatoribus in locum Abbatis <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-104058412">Viali</rs>, qui (ut dicere
  <lb/>solent) jubilatus est sed ista electio licet probata <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> Collegio Sapientum,
  <lb/>non delata fuit ad Senatum, id quod min<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> potentum et artes
  <lb/>inimicorum (ne dicam amicorum) nostrorum effecerunt. In ejus
  <lb/>locum <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs type="persons">Reformatoribus</rs> et <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> Senatu Pontedera quidam, ju<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>venis sed cliens Eminentissimi electus fuit cum
  <pb facs="1038153" n="4"/>
  stipendio 200. florenorum. Canonicus <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1158980426">Giacometti</rs> Professor noster <abbr>Phil.</abbr>
  <lb/> <abbr>Mor.</abbr> quem ad sanam mentem reciturum non putabant (ita enim malefe<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>riatus erat, ut sibi met manus violentas intulerit) Professionem suam
  <lb/>nuper auspicatus est coram incredibili multitudine auditorum.</p>
<closer>Vale. 
  <lb/><dateline><abbr>D.</abbr> <abbr>Pat.</abbr> <date when="1719-04-01">1. Apr. 1719</date>.</dateline></closer>
